{"tid":1377920,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你班勇武同和理非都入來講講講Be Water 定義","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T15:44:31.000Z","uid":158873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"413e450bfcfce41b7104f5da2ed54f7d7f86e4d9","tid":1377920,"uid":158873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:51:14.000Z","msg":"純分析 請大家留言<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好割蓆/屌7大家</span>既行動<br />\n見連登開始和理非同勇武屌7大家 <br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以<span style=\"color: red;\">討論一下</span> 或者 <span style=\"color: red;\">互相理解</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">畢竟大家都係想為件事好<br />\n</span></span><br />\n個人認為 和理非同勇武對於 Be Water 既定義唔同<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非</span>：唔好同警察玩咁耐 佢哋上曬gear就走 令佢哋谷住谷住 咁就最好玩 因為無傷害又玩9佢哋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>：獨立思考 唔死守一個大台的思考 所以覺得係現場可以同警方繼續玩 就會繼續留低 直接搵搞警察<br />\n<br />\n（個人意見 未必完全岩 請大家開放討論）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0b115ff49d341205b45d79f28599738606c18a","tid":1377920,"uid":158873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:52:13.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"79b7652b46abed0eeebfacf62831ddf0d3fc6b6b","tid":1377920,"uid":24776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MufSfFD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMufSfFD.png&h=832e449b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c425f1e0aeef756feb91da3068b5f42f2dffff8f","tid":1377920,"uid":158873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:53:42.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"5cf6b13725d72ba69820d32fe5ef89664797cd84","tid":1377920,"uid":158873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:54:14.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"03aca9d394c7175627aa2abf55fda76e37c7bac2","tid":1377920,"uid":65887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:56:04.000Z"